  Uploaded by : clockdryve <clockdryve@...> 
  Description : Got this at 7am in back yard (get many evp's here) is old timey as the little girl says "paw" the woman speaks in a robotic-warble tone. I say "where'd she go" I was talking about a female Cardinal Bird that flew off a telephone pole. Is very low audio-should hear Big Girl though. Play 3 or 4 times with headphones will help.
